<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>xiāng xìn shén de xìn shí 迦南1341</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 xiāng xìn shén de xìn shí xiāng xìn shén de xìn shí nǐ jiù bù huì yōu chóu
 xiāng xìn shén de xìn shí xiāng xìn shén de xìn shí nǐ jiù bù huì jù pà
 xiāng xìn shén de yīng xǔ xiāng xìn shén de yīng xǔ nǐ jiù bù huì yáo dòng
 xiāng xìn shén de yīng xǔ xiāng xìn shén de yīng xǔ nǐ jiù chōng mǎn pàn wàng
 zhǔ de cí ài shàng jí zhū tiān tā de xìn shí dá dào qióng cāng
 tā shì zhǎng guǎn wàn yǒu de zhǔ zǎi tā zuì zhí dé wǒ men xìn kào</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1341</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>